s($,"aQI","aqJ",()=>A.b([A.hF("assets/images/news/news1.webp","Como abrebocas de lo que ser\xe1 este nuevo album Nueva Timba, el aclamado pianista cubano Harold L\xf3pez Nussa nos presenta Bonito... ","11 july 2025","https://www.solarlatinclub.com/harold-lopez-nussa-nueva-timba/","CUBADEBATE","Harold L\xf3pez-Nussa - Nueva Timba"),A.hF("assets/images/news/news2.webp","La m\xfasica latina fue un descubrimiento para el bop, que sonaba muy oscuro a veces, con su complejidad arm\xf3nica y la profundidad del blues que imprimi\xf3 Charlie Parke","2 november 2025","https://www.granadahoy.com/ocio/virtuosismo-esencias-habana-critica-musica_0_2005149930.html","Granada Hoy","Virtuosismo y esencias de La Habana."),A.hF("assets/images/news/news4.webp","Sometimes maintaining tradition while breathing new life into old modes is challenging. Pianist/composer L\xf3pez Nussa seems delight","november 25","https://drive.google.com/file/d/1bTeWJjJ_WgtWyBmom-nNNgpDwN1nzl19/view?usp=drive_link","DOWNBEAT","Harold L\xf3pez-Nussa \u201cNueva Timba\u201d"),A.hF("assets/images/news/news5.webp","Jazz is renowed for his constant renowned, so it\xb4s odd that Afro-Cuban jazz has barely changed since Gizzy Gillespie, Machito and others ","6 september 2023",u.m,"THE TIMES","Timba a la americana rewiew / the future of Latin Jazz")],A.a4("q<ki>")))
